Meaning: Near constraint boundary.
Prosoetic:
Edges ring —
step light.

v23 — Texture Weighting Rule

Geometry: multiplier(texture)
Meaning: Adjust search by state.
Prosoetic:
Walk soft in mud —
firm on steel.

v24 — Binding Cost Accounting

Geometry: E_bind tracked
Meaning: Coherence consumes capacity.
Prosoetic:
Holding shape
burns fuel.

v25 — Ridge Navigation

Geometry: maximize stability between basins
Meaning: Stay between chaos and rigidity.
Prosoetic:
Walk the spine —
not the cliff
nor the swamp.

v26 — Drift Re-Annealing

Geometry: mix_hot/cool passes
Meaning: Revisit old clusters periodically.
Prosoetic:
Turn the soil —
old seeds rise.

v27 — Coherence Invariant

Geometry: det(ℛ) ≠ 0
Meaning: Preserve relational structure.
Prosoetic:
If the web holds —
the path remains.
